title: President Obama went to prison today-- | On Air Videos | Fox News
text:
Live President Obama went to prison today-- 
Jul. 16, 2015 - 0:57 - President Obama went to prison today. He traveled to El Reno Federal Correctional Institution near Oklahoma City to talk about criminal justice reform. He becomes the first sitting president to go inside a federal prison. Fox Business Channel Finder
